{"tid":1526273,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"SOS香港已需救災","createTime":"2019-09-01T05:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T05:16:34.000Z","uid":283222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2a8d1896c584236c550aafc2e9a673e0c1021e6e","tid":1526273,"uid":283222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:08:17.000Z","msg":"近日已見正苦及警方變本加厲非人道對待示威者，義務及醫院醫護又大受打壓，受傷示威者傷勢又越加嚴重，還很多敢到院求診，有冇能人巴打，絲可將此災難向國際救援組織求助。例如:紅十字會，樂施會&hellip;&hellip;等。香港的怕已被打壓，而且暴力打壓越嚟越嚴重。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7262ce9078853daed3191d3e72af5ab0a60cbe","tid":1526273,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:09:13.000Z","msg":"點證明？"},{"pid":"c588507a525a5728792595d31e64d0786ba49276","tid":1526273,"uid":177336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:09:23.000Z","msg":"901 機場攻略<br />\n麻煩大家用盡所有方法傳開佢<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">準時</span>到機場，唔係一點先出門口<br />\n- 衣着同裝備冇任何限制，最緊要保護自己<br />\n- 集合地點：機場巴士總站(暢達路)<br />\n- 測試方法：排隊戰術，見到<span style=\"color: red;\">有隊就排</span>；利用人數優勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好單獨行事</span><br />\n- 唔好同任何遊客有肢體碰撞<br />\n- 去機場：<span style=\"color: red;\">以巴士為優先</span>，機場快線集中係香港同青衣站上車<br />\n- 已經準備左幾套應變方案，根據現場情況<span style=\"color: red;\">隨時轉變</span>，要密切留意住 901 機場 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2X5ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=82afd802\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5XusdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5XusdO.jpg&h=31adcd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTXKf68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTXKf68.jpg&h=74d57433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAxaV7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAxaV7a.jpg&h=13c2eb06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otZAnNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotZAnNa.jpg&h=f10fa124&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed80f00d2280ab148a35a54289f89125abac9859","tid":1526273,"uid":283222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee7262ce9078853daed3191d3e72af5ab0a60cbe","tid":1526273,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:09:13.000Z","msg":"點證明？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:13:28.000Z","msg":"唔識，最主要係想將佢擺上國際，唔好俾中共收收埋埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ca7da2b93ee580f5f800f992568a06e95ffd27","tid":1526273,"uid":283222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34cdae43eb8718e6c51b75a3514694d8f6f7f58b","tid":1526273,"uid":283222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:13:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42bfe44e72deba1a0c7d4a18768f58db182096b3","tid":1526273,"uid":283222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e697b68d5f58d3d86f939bb77469f37208160c","tid":1526273,"uid":283222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee7262ce9078853daed3191d3e72af5ab0a60cbe","tid":1526273,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:09:13.000Z","msg":"點證明？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:15:30.000Z","msg":"諗到樣係警方之曱甴論，唔知有冇用？"},{"pid":"0b50b6854ae1579fb07d13b